==Punctuation

    The first letter of a sentence is punctuated. Inline quotations are
indicated using quotes, "like this".
    --- As for dialog, well, it's done like this...
    --- Oh, I see, that's common across other languages, right?
    --- Yes, it is.
    The other punctuation marks used are commas, full stops, semicolons, colons,
ellipses, and parentheses. Their usages are the same as in English.

