===Agent nouns

    Agent nouns are formed through reduplication of the last syllable, with the
removal of the C1 and (if present) C2. For example:

*Kukьon --- professional cooking
*Kukьonon --- chef
*Lesьapь --- professional driving
*Lesьapьapь --- driver
*Kьobьet --- romantic love
*Kьobьetet -- lover

