===Negation

    Negation is achieved through reduplication of the first syllable, with the
removal of the (if present) C3. For example:

*Rogod --- murder
*Rorogod --- not murder
*Zьen --- be
*Zьezьen --- not be
*Kkьuno --- cook professionally
*Kkьukkьuno --- not cook professionally

===Reflexive verbs

    Reflexive verbs are formed through reduplication of the last syllable, with
the removal of the C1 and (if present) C2. For example:

*Rogod --- murder
*Rogodod --- kill oneself
*Kьebьot --- love
*Kьebьotot --- self-obsess

